<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Privacy Policy - LuxeClean</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" />
  <style>
    /* Local layout styling for privacy page */
    .privacy-container {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      padding: 20px 30px;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #333;
    }

    .privacy-container h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .privacy-container h2 {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      margin: 30px 0 10px;
    }

    .privacy-container p {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .navbar {
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="privacy-body">

  <!-- Main site navigation -->
  <div class="navbar">
    <nav>
      <a class="btn" href="/">Home</a>
      <% if (user) { %>
      <a class="btn" href="/price-list">Price List</a>
      <a class="btn" href="/cart">Cart</a>
    <% } %>
      <a class="btn" href="/contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>
  </div>

  <div class="privacy-container">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p>
      LuxeClean values your privacy. This policy explains how we collect and use personal information when you use our services.
    </p>

    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>Depending on your activity, we may collect:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Your name, email address, and phone number</li>
      <li>Payment details (securely handled via Stripe)</li>
      <li>Your order history and preferences</li>
      <li>Technical info like browser type and IP address</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. How We Use Your Data</h2>
    <p>We use it to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Manage orders and customer accounts</li>
      <li>Send confirmations and updates</li>
      <li>Improve the overall user experience</li>
      <li>Respond to support requests</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Data Security</h2>
    <p>
      We take security seriously — all data is encrypted, stored securely, and only accessible to authorized staff.
    </p>

    <h2>4. Sharing Information</h2>
    <p>
      Your data isn't sold or rented. We may share it with trusted partners like Stripe to complete your transactions.
    </p>

    <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You can always:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Request access to your data</li>
      <li>Correct or delete your info</li>
      <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>6. Cookies</h2>
    <p>
      We use cookies to personalize your experience. You can disable them in your browser if preferred.
    </p>

    <h2>7. Retention</h2>
    <p>
      We retain your data only as long as needed for legal or business reasons.
    </p>

    <h2>8. External Links</h2>
    <p>
      Some pages may link to other websites. We’re not responsible for their privacy practices.
    </p>

    <h2>9. Updates</h2>
    <p>
      From time to time, we may revise this policy. The current version will always be posted here.
    </p>

    <h2>10. Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Questions? Reach us at <strong>support@luxeclean.com</strong>.
    </p>

    <p><em>Last updated: April 2025</em></p>
  </div>

  <footer class="footer">
    <p>&copy; 2025 LuxeClean. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
